Olympics; Canada, Mexico, and Australia formed the Axis of Nations That<br>
Are<br>
Actually Quite Nice But Secretly Have Nasty Thoughts About America, while<br>
Spain, Scotland, and New Zealand established the Axis of Countries That<br>
Sometimes Ask Sheep to Wear Lipstick.<br>
&quot;That's not a threat, really, just something we like to do,&quot; said Scottish<br>
Executive First Minister Jack McConnell.<br>
